{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"type":"conformsTo"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSSwitchItem","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Layouts","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Layouts"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"inverse","type":"text"}]},{"text":": like the ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}]},{"text":" layout but with a trailing switch indicator and a leading optional decorative icon","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Indicator states","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Indicator-states"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The switch indicator has two available states set as a boolean property that determines whether the toggle is on or off."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Particular cases","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem","type":"reference"},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In addition, the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem","type":"reference"},{"text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as disabled.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The switch can be also outlined in some cases.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom switch trait."}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","level":2,"text":"Forbidden by design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2,"text":"Code samples"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var isOn: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, and an helper text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, helper: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A leading switch with an additional label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\", helper: \"1967\")","","    \/\/ A trailing switch with a label, an additonal label, an helper text and an icon.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\",","                   helper: \"1967\",","                   isReversed: true,","                   icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ A trailing switch with a label, an helper text, an icon, a divider and is about an error.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   helper: \"Put your hand in mine\",","                   icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"),","                   isReversed: true,","                   isError: true,","                   hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\", isOn: $isOn)","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related switch as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $isOn, isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $isOn, isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/18acc0-switch","type":"reference","isActive":true}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Themes rendering","anchor":"Themes-rendering","level":2},{"type":"heading","text":"Orange","anchor":"Orange","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_switchitem_enabled_selected_Orange","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Orange Business Tools","anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_switchitem_enabled_selected_OrangeBusinessTools"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Orange Inverse","anchor":"Orange-Inverse","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_switchitem_enabled_selected_OrangeInverse","type":"image"}]},{"text":"Sosh","type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_switchitem_enabled_selected_Sosh"}]},{"text":"Wireframe","type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_switchitem_enabled_selected_Wireframe"}]},{"type":"aside","name":"Version","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.1.0 (Figma component design version)"}]}]},{"type":"aside","name":"Since","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.14.0","type":"text"}]}]}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchI